wiki.content: Amy wrote this song the day after seeing Peter Doherty perform at the glasgow barrowland. Amy wrote 'This Is The Life' after blagging her way into a Babyshambles after-party, having a brilliant time and thinking “this is the life”! The 20 year old Scots lass is completely self taught and has come a long way from her days performing at her local coffee shop's open-mic night!
